title: (x) Cabo Wabo - Birch {Patricia}
content:
Once again, I have to work with an existing brand and I have no access to anyone involved with the business. Can anyone identify the font that "Cabo Wabo" is set in? Or give me a hint towards a font that I can use that will appear similar enough to an undiscerning web audience?   
   
Thank you very much!
